  "content": "Just when you thought the days of web directories were over... that speculative blog post by Fluent Simplicity listing a few of the brands with Twitter feeds is reborn - as a standalone site at Social Brand Index. I still say a publicly editable wiki would be far more practical. Still, a glance down the page of represented brands is quite interesting, and there are several hundred listed. Photo by tashmahal on Flickr. Some rights reserved. Jonathan [Namelostintransit] has organised listings by industry genre and also a section for official brand feeds managed in-house. To be added, email him."
